{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a172533cb6","title":"注意利用日蒋矛盾粉碎顽军的进攻可","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"616149bb40","index":0,"year":1941,"month":1,"day":13,"articleId":"a172533cb6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji15.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji15":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ead590b761","type":"paragraph","text":"注意利用日蒋矛盾粉碎顽军的进攻可","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"a172533cb6"},{"id":"1e5f9853d1","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年1月13日）有情报证明淮南路日军撤退全是谣传，蒋、桂对日军仍是敌对的。据去春背东经验，我打朱怀冰后，蒋调集大军正准备通过音城、长治线向太行山我军进攻之际，被日军集中“扫荡”，将各反共军打得七零八落。同时日军在皖南、鄂西采取攻势，反共高潮因面下降。此种经验，你们很可利用，但不要因此松解自己准备。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"a172533cb6"}],"page":{"id":"a8faabc616","publicationId":"maoquanji15","articleId":"a172533cb6","start":336,"end":336}}}},"__N_SSG":true}